{"id": "1189167225219850301", "channel_id": "1189147235208933397", "type": 0, "author_id": "788966489000378398", "author_name": "pppggg12", "author_bot": false, "content": "我只是很喜愛這個遊戲\n但是我真的不擅長 \n這個我承認\nPVP那邊要升到資深才有的銀幣獎勵我已經放棄了 \n我也只能心裏承認 只是因為我弱，所以拿不到也算了", "timestamp": "2023-12-26T11:26:00.151000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189147235208933397", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌薩格攻略研讀會」募集中！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
