{"id": "1189167703701868576", "channel_id": "1189147235208933397", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@788966489000378398> 看官方的意思应该是每月发布攻略的奖励，不追溯过往的攻略。这样的话用玩家劳动换取报酬我觉得非常合理呀", "timestamp": "2023-12-26T11:27:54.230000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["788966489000378398"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189147235208933397", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌薩格攻略研讀會」募集中！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
