{"id": "1189167917724618762", "channel_id": "1189147235208933397", "type": 19, "author_id": "1179254146482847824", "author_name": "alpha0909__", "author_bot": false, "content": "並不是永久的福利喔~我們還是會有要求研讀會的成員每月進行一定的基礎要求，例如攻略的生產、攻略大賽的評分事項協助、以及攻略分享等等事項~", "timestamp": "2023-12-26T11:28:45.257000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["788966489000378398"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1189167225219850301", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189147235208933397", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌薩格攻略研讀會」募集中！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
{"id": "1189168127062319144", "channel_id": "1189147235208933397", "type": 19, "author_id": "788966489000378398", "author_name": "pppggg12", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果有投稿 然後符合字數要求那些 就能得到獎勵的話，才是勞動換取報酬吧", "timestamp": "2023-12-26T11:29:35.167000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1181025751710056449"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1189167703701868576", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189147235208933397", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌薩格攻略研讀會」募集中！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
{"id": "1189168586632204339", "channel_id": "1189147235208933397", "type": 19, "author_id": "788966489000378398", "author_name": "pppggg12", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後請問官方是不是每月發佈攻略？\n這個我看的意思是只要這次入選了他永久就有", "timestamp": "2023-12-26T11:31:24.737000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1181025751710056449"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1189167703701868576", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189147235208933397", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌薩格攻略研讀會」募集中！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
{"id": "1189168728907198474", "channel_id": "1189147235208933397", "type": 19, "author_id": "788966489000378398", "author_name": "pppggg12", "author_bot": false, "content": "他是只挑天選之人的勞動才是勞動", "timestamp": "2023-12-26T11:31:58.658000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1189168127062319144", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189147235208933397", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌薩格攻略研讀會」募集中！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
